<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<task id="060" project="spaarke-matter-ui-enhancement-r1">
  <metadata>
    <title>Matter form Overview tab 2-column 66/34 layout (FR-FORM-01)</title>
    <phase>6: Form Configuration</phase>
    <status>not-started</status>
    <estimated-hours>3-4</estimated-hours>
    <dependencies>024, 030, 031, 032, 033, 034, 040</dependencies>
    <blocks>073</blocks>
    <tags>dataverse, solution, form-xml</tags>
    <rigor-hint>FULL</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>Solution XML edits to a production form with multiple Visual Host instances + Semantic Search PCF binding; has explicit constraints (FR-FORM-01, NFR-03), depends on 7 upstream tasks, error rollback is non-trivial.</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>none</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>false</parallel-safe>
    <parallel-reason>Single form XML target; downstream blocker for 073 solution import; depends on completion of all chart definitions and CardChrome wrapping.</parallel-reason>
  </metadata>

  <prompt>
    Reconfigure the Matter main-form Overview tab to a 2-column 66/34 layout per FR-FORM-01. Left column (66%): Matter Information section (native MDA, 2 sub-columns: Matter Number / Matter Name / Matter Type / Practice Area / Matter Description), then a Documents section bound to the Semantic Search PCF. Right column (34%): Matter Performance section containing 5 stacked Visual Host instances — one per `sprk_chartdefinition` lookup (Matter Health, Matter Budget, Matter Tasks, Matter Next Date, Matter Activity). Header section unchanged. Other tabs untouched.
  </prompt>

  <role>
    Dataverse solution author with deep familiarity with model-driven app FormXml (`SystemForm.formxml`), section column ratios, control bindings, and PCF custom-control parameter wiring. Comfortable with the export → unpack → edit XML → pack → import flow.
  </role>

  <goal>
    The Matter main form's Overview tab XML reflects the FR-FORM-01 layout. Five `&lt;control&gt;` elements bind Visual Host instances to the 5 chart-definition lookups. The Documents section binds to the Semantic Search PCF. Layout renders 2-column at viewport ≥1024 px (verified post-import in task 073). The solution containing the updated FormXml is staged and ready for import via task 073.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      FR-FORM-01 is the final composition step before deploy. All renderer extensions (tasks 020-024), the CardChrome wrapper (024), the 5 chart definitions (030-034), and the Documents PCF behavioral changes (040+) ship first; this task wires them into the form. Per spec.md §Assumptions #3, the Matter main form is assumed to live in the unmanaged Spaarke solution that's also the deployment target — verify during Step 1 and adjust the export source if it lives elsewhere.
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>(Spaarke unmanaged solution) — Matter main form FormXml (path determined at Step 1)</file>
      <file>src/client/pcf/VisualHost/control/ControlManifest.Input.xml</file>
      <file>src/client/pcf/SemanticSearchControl/SemanticSearchControl/ControlManifest.Input.xml</file>
    </relevant-files>
  </context>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="spec">FR-FORM-01 — 2-column 66/34 layout at viewport ≥1024 px</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec">FR-FORM-01 — left col: Matter Information (2 sub-cols, native MDA section) + Documents section bound to Semantic Search PCF</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec">FR-FORM-01 — right col: Matter Performance section with 5 stacked Visual Host instances; each bound via its sprk_chartdefinition lookup</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec">FR-FORM-01 — header section unchanged; other tabs unchanged</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec">NFR-03 — hard minimum 1024 px desktop; right rail compresses without overflow or stacking</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec">§Out of Scope — no AI Summary banner in header (deferred to r2)</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-021">UI uses Fluent v9 tokens — verified at renderer level; this task is XML only</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>.claude/skills/dataverse-deploy/SKILL.md</file>
      <file>.claude/skills/dataverse-create-schema/SKILL.md</file>
      <file>projects/spaarke-matter-ui-enhancement-r1/spec.md</file>
      <file>projects/spaarke-matter-ui-enhancement-r1/design.md</file>
      <file>src/client/pcf/VisualHost/control/ControlManifest.Input.xml</file>
      <file>src/client/pcf/SemanticSearchControl/SemanticSearchControl/ControlManifest.Input.xml</file>
    </files>
    <patterns>
      <pattern name="FormXml section column ratio" location="(Matter main form FormXml)">
        Use `&lt;section&gt;` with `columns="66,34"` (or equivalent `colspan` distribution) for the 2-column layout. Native MDA section under the left col uses default 2-sub-column layout.
      </pattern>
      <pattern name="Visual Host PCF binding" location="src/client/pcf/VisualHost/control/ControlManifest.Input.xml">
        Each Visual Host instance binds the chart-definition lookup to the host control's `chartDefinitionId` (or equivalent) parameter; verify exact parameter name in the manifest.
      </pattern>
      <pattern name="Semantic Search PCF binding" location="src/client/pcf/SemanticSearchControl/SemanticSearchControl/ControlManifest.Input.xml">
        Documents section binds the Semantic Search control to the Matter record context (`apiBaseUrl`, `tenantId`, `clientAppId`, `bffAppId`, `appInsightsKey` from task 002).
      </pattern>
    </patterns>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="0">Locate the source-of-truth solution containing the Matter main form. Per spec.md §Assumptions #3, presumed to be the unmanaged Spaarke solution; verify with `pac solution list` and `pac solution online-version`. If the form lives in a managed-only solution, BLOCK and request human input (Section 6 of CLAUDE.md).</step>
    <step order="1">Export the source solution as unmanaged using `pac solution export --name {SolutionName} --managed false`. Unpack with `pac solution unpack` to a working folder.</step>
    <step order="2">Locate the Matter main form FormXml file (typically `Entities/sprk_matter/FormXml/main/main.xml` or similar). Snapshot the current file before editing.</step>
    <step order="3">Edit the Overview tab section structure: introduce a 2-column section with `columns="66,34"`. Preserve header section verbatim. Preserve all other tabs verbatim.</step>
    <step order="4">In the left (66%) column, add: (a) Matter Information section using native MDA with 2 sub-columns binding `sprk_matternumber`, `sprk_mattername`, `sprk_mattertype`, `sprk_practicearea`, `sprk_matterdescription`; (b) Documents section with a control element binding the Semantic Search PCF to the form context. Confirm manifest parameter names (`apiBaseUrl`, `tenantId`, `clientAppId`, `bffAppId`, `appInsightsKey`) are wired with env-var bindings.</step>
    <step order="5">In the right (34%) column, add a Matter Performance section containing 5 stacked control elements, each binding the Visual Host PCF to one of the 5 `sprk_chartdefinition` lookups: Matter Health (030), Matter Budget (031), Matter Tasks (032), Matter Next Date (033), Matter Activity (034). Confirm the manifest parameter name for the chart-def lookup matches the Visual Host `ControlManifest.Input.xml`.</step>
    <step order="6">Re-pack the solution with `pac solution pack`. Validate the resulting solution zip with `pac solution check` (if available) to catch obvious FormXml errors before import.</step>
    <step order="7">Stage the packed solution for task 073 (import). Do NOT import in this task — import is a deploy step gated by 070, 071, 072.</step>
    <step order="8">Step 9.5 (FULL rigor): run `Skill code-review` + `Skill adr-check` against the changed FormXml + any related manifest changes. Resolve issues.</step>
    <step order="9">Update TASK-INDEX.md: 060 → ✅. Reset current-task.md for next pending task.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="pac">Power Platform CLI — solution export/unpack/pack</tool>
    <tool name="dataverse-deploy">Skill for solution operations</tool>
    <tool name="git">Snapshot FormXml before editing; track diff</tool>
  </tools>

  <outputs>
    <output type="solution">{solution-name}/Entities/sprk_matter/FormXml/main/main.xml (updated)</output>
    <output type="solution">Packed solution zip staged for task 073 import</output>
    <output type="docs">projects/spaarke-matter-ui-enhancement-r1/tasks/TASK-INDEX.md (status update)</output>
  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">The Matter main form FormXml contains a 2-column section with 66/34 ratio at the top of the Overview tab.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Left column contains Matter Information section (native MDA, 2 sub-columns, 5 fields per spec) and Documents section with a control element binding the Semantic Search PCF.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Right column contains a Matter Performance section with 5 control elements, each binding a Visual Host instance to one of the 5 chart-definition lookups (Health/Budget/Tasks/NextDate/Activity).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Header section is byte-identical to the pre-edit version; other tabs are byte-identical.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`pac solution pack` succeeds without errors; solution zip is staged at a known path for task 073.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`code-review` + `adr-check` pass.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    This task is XML-only. Render verification happens in task 073 (post-import) and task 074 (NFR-01..05 validation). If the chart-def lookup parameter name differs from the assumption above, fall back to reading `src/client/pcf/VisualHost/control/ControlManifest.Input.xml` directly — the manifest is the source of truth for parameter names.

    If the Matter main form lives in a different solution than the deployment target solution, this task's strategy must change to a cross-solution merge — escalate to human input rather than guess.
  </notes>

  <execution>
    <skill>.claude/skills/task-execute/SKILL.md</skill>
    <protocol>
      FULL rigor. Step 0.5 is NOT applicable (no Fluent v9 component authoring — XML only). Load knowledge (dataverse-deploy skill, spec.md, both PCF manifests). Export + unpack solution. Edit FormXml. Re-pack. Stage for task 073. Step 9.5: run code-review + adr-check on the FormXml diff. Update TASK-INDEX.
    </protocol>
  </execution>
</task>
